{"title":"「推荐」本站用到的 hexo 插件","slug":"hello-world","date":"2021-09-04T10:09:59.107Z","updated":"2021-09-04T10:09:59.107Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hello-world.json","excerpt":"悬浮注释 hintnpm install hexo-tag-hint --save&#123;% hint '这里是正文' '这里是注释 :D' %&#125;&lt;br&gt; # 换行判定好像有问题，必须手动加 br 标签&#123;% hint 'I\\'m Groot' 'I\\'m Groot' %&#125;这里是正文下拉抽屉&#123;% details Where are you from? %&#125;I'm from the Earth. Water Planet!&#123;% enddetails %&#125;","covers":["https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/XuxuGood/cdn@master/blogImages/resume/resumeBg.jpg","https://github-readme-stats.vercel.app/api/?username=win-keep199&show_owner=true"],"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text&#x2F;css\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/hexo-tag-hint@0.3.1/dist/hexo-tag-hint.min.css\"><h3 id=\"悬浮注释-hint\"><a href=\"#悬浮注释-hint\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"悬浮注释 hint\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/etigerstudio/hexo-tag-hint\">悬浮注释 hint</a></h3><p><code>npm install hexo-tag-hint --save</code></p>\n<pre><code>&#123;% hint '这里是正文' '这里是注释 :D' %&#125;\n&lt;br&gt; # 换行判定好像有问题，必须手动加 br 标签\n&#123;% hint 'I\\'m Groot' 'I\\'m Groot' %&#125;\n</code></pre><span class=\"hint--info hint--rounded hint--top\" data-hint=\"这里是注释 :D\" ontouchstart>这里是正文</span>\n<h3 id=\"下拉抽屉\"><a href=\"#下拉抽屉\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下拉抽屉\"></a>下拉抽屉</h3><pre><code>&#123;% details Where are you from? %&#125;\nI'm from the Earth. Water Planet!\n&#123;% enddetails %&#125;\n</code></pre><span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h3 id=\"文字遮盖效果-Spoiler\"><a href=\"#文字遮盖效果-Spoiler\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文字遮盖效果 Spoiler\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/unnamed42/hexo-spoiler\">文字遮盖效果 Spoiler</a></h3><p><code>npm install hexo-spoiler --save</code></p>\n<p>站点根目录配置填写</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-yaml\">spoiler:\n  style: blur # 或者box\n  color: black # 仅当 style 为 box 时起效\n  p: false # 没懂啥意思，不管它\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>&#123;% spoiler option:value text... %&#125;</code></p>\n<p><code>&#123;% spoiler 默认配置效果 %&#125;</code> → <!-- spoiler-1ffd9:black -->\n  <span class=\"spoiler\" onclick=\"this.classList.toggle('spoiler')\">\n    <span class=\"spoiler-blur spoiler-1ffd9\">默认配置效果</span>\n  </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"动态终端代码演示\"><a href=\"#动态终端代码演示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"动态终端代码演示\"></a><a href=\"https://github.com/heowc/hexo-tag-gdemo\">动态终端代码演示</a></h3><p><code>npm install @heowc/hexo-tag-gdemo</code></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://heowc.dev/2018/11/14/introduction-hexo-tag-gdemo/\">介绍及效果预览</a></p>\n<pre><code>&#123;% gdemo_terminal command [最小高度] [窗口标题] [延迟时间] [提示字符] [唯一id] [高亮语言] %&#125;\ncontent\n&#123;% endgdemo_terminal %&#125;\n</code></pre><pre><code>&#123;% gdemo_terminal 'node ./demo' '250px' 'bash' '500' '$' 'demo-teriminal' %&#125;\nHello World!\n&#123;% endgdemo_terminal %&#125;\n</code></pre><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@glorious/demo@0.11.4/dist/gdemo.min.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/prismjs/themes/prism-tomorrow.css\">\n<script src=\"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@glorious/demo@0.11.4/dist/gdemo.min.js\"></script>\n<div id='demo-teriminal' style='height: 250px'></div>\n<script>\nnew GDemo('#demo-teriminal')\n  .openApp('terminal', {minHeight: '250px', windowTitle: 'bash', promptString: '$'})\n  .command(`cd <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>usr<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>bin`, {onCompleteDelay: 500})\n  .command(`<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>node <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>demo`, {onCompleteDelay: 500})\n  .respond(`Hello World!`)\n  .end();\n</script>\n<h3 id=\"pdf\"><a href=\"#pdf\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"pdf\"></a>pdf</h3><p><code>npm install --save hexo-pdf</code></p>\n<pre><code>&#123;% pdf http://7xov2f.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/bash_freshman.pdf %&#125;\n&#123;% pdf ./bash_freshman.pdf %&#125;\n&#123;% pdf https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B6qSwdwPxPRdTEliX0dhQ2JfUEU/preview %&#125;\n</code></